Package: EnSDD
Type: Package
Title: EnSDD: spatial domain detection in spatial transcriptomics data via ensemble learning
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Huisheng,Li and Yuting,Tan
Maintainer: Huisheng,Li and Yuting,Tan <lihs@zjut.edu.cn>
Description: EnSDD mainly is designed for the dection of spatial domain for SRT data. 
             Leveraging the information of spatial domain of tissue, EnSDD also enables to 
             detect domain-specific spatially variable genes and infer the spatial distribution of cell type.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), dplyr
Imports: Seurat,
         parallel,
         abind,
         SingleCellExperiment,
         scran,
         scater,
         BayesSpace,
         DR.SC,
         mclust,
         reticulate,
         spdep,
         spacexr,
         igraph, 
         ggplot2,
         ggrepel,
         ggpubr, 
         reshape2, 
         networkD3
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
